    <fr:title text="Jacobi Identity">Jacobi Identity</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>definition</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n\in \mathbb {N}]]></fr:tex> be a positive integer, let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {A}]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {B}]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {C}]]></fr:tex> be <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n\times  n]]></fr:tex> matrices over a <fr:link href="/field-0001/" title="Field" uri="http://localhost:8000/field-0001/" display-uri="field-0001" type="local">Field</fr:link> (or a <fr:link href="/ring-0001/" title="Ring" uri="http://localhost:8000/ring-0001/" display-uri="ring-0001" type="local">ring</fr:link> or...). Then we define the <html:dfn>Jacobi Identity</html:dfn> to be the condition
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[[\mathbf {A},[\mathbf {B},\mathbf {C}]] + [\mathbf {B}, [\mathbf {C}, \mathbf {A}]] + [\mathbf {C}, [\mathbf {A}, \mathbf {B}]] = 0.]]></fr:tex></html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
